data.description: This home and property have been impeccably maintained! Enter the home thru the curved archway and covered front porch to the large open den with fireplace and light and airy kitchen that includes an oversized breakfast island, enormous pantry, granite countertops, tile backsplash and all stainless steel appliances and dining area. The master bedroom that is located just off the kitchen/den is spacious and has and plenty of light.  Just off the master you will find an oversized bath room with a walk in closet, double vanity, huge tiled shower and separate tub and powder room. Additional bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the kitchen and are comfortably sized with a guest bath between them.  A separate laundry room and mud room complete the home and exit to a covered patio.  Additional features include plantation shutters on EVERY window, whole house water filtration system. irrigation system, spacious garage, amazing landscaping and a tool room out back.
